7B%22title%22%3A%22Here%20are%209%20cheap%20but%20solid%20names%20to%20buy%20now%20as%20AI%20stocks%20enter%20bear%20market%20territory%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20robot%20sitting%20on%20a%20pile%20of%20cash%2C%20a%20Wall%20Street%20sign%2C%20and%20a%20downward%20stock%20arrow.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672bbeb0192f5258985684e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPhonlamaiPhoto%2FGetty%2C%20mbbirdy%2FGetty%2C%20Richard%20Darko%2FGetty%2C%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20stocks%20are%20declining%20as%20market%20volatility%20increases%20and%20investor%20caution%20grows.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20good%20news%20is%20that%20some%20of%20these%20formerly%20expensive%20companies%20are%20now%20in%20fair-value%20territory.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENames%20like%20Microsoft%2C%20Adobe%2C%20and%20ServiceNow%20are%20solid%20names%20and%20well-priced.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20believe%20that%20AI%20stocks%20are%20now%20in%20a%20bear%20market%20since%20many%20have%20fallen%20by%20more%20than%2020%25%20from%20their%20highs.%20It%20comes%20after%20a%20multi-year%20run%20that%20lifted%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20about%2024%25%20in%202023%20and%2023%25%20in%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20script%20has%20flipped%2C%20and%20the%20index%20is%20being%20held%20up%20by%20the%20broader%20market%20instead%20of%20the%20Magnificent%207.%20As%20of%20Thursday%2C%20the%20two%20largest%20stocks%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnvda-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENvidia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Faapl-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EApple%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20were%20down%20by%20almost%2014%25%20and%2012%25%2C%20respectively%20this%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20well-known%20AI%20plays%20followed%20closely%20behind.%20As%20of%20Thursday%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Favgo-stock%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBroadcom%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20down%20by%20over%2017%25%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Farista_networks-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EArista%20Networks%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%2025%25%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmrvl-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMarvell%20Technology%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20over%2037%25%20this%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDeepSeek's%20debut%2C%20which%20introduced%20a%20software-efficient%20solution%20to%20investors%20in%20late%20January%2C%20marked%20a%20peak%20reversal%20for%20this%20sector.%20A%20new%20reality%20has%20kicked%20in%3A%20Big%20Tech%20isn't%20immune%20to%20market%20competition%2C%20which%20is%20causing%20investors%20to%20sober%20up%20from%20their%20valuation-induced%20highs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20essentially%20seen%20the%20AI%20stocks%20on%20a%20downward%20trend%20ever%20since%20then%2C%20said%20Dave%20Sekera%2C%20Morningstar's%20chief%20US%20market%20strategist.%20%26quot%3BMost%20of%20those%20stocks%20have%20sold%20off%20anywhere%20between%2015%25%20to%2020%25.%20So%20pretty%20close%20to%20what%20would%20be%20considered%20a%20bear%20market%20in%20AI%20stocks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERisk-off%20moves%20followed%20the%20reversal%20as%20economic%20fears%20mounted%20from%20trade%20wars%20and%20slowing%20GDP%20growth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bad%20news%20is%2C%20if%20you%20have%20heavy%20exposure%20to%20AI%2C%20you're%20portfolio%20is%20likely%20down.%20The%20good%20news%20is%20that%20some%20of%20these%20formerly%20expensive%20companies%20are%20now%20in%20fair-value%20territory%2C%20according%20to%20Morningstar's%20five-star%20valuation%20system%2C%20which%20considers%20a%20company's%20fundamentals%20relative%20to%20its%20trading%20price.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20year%2C%20Sekera%20expects%20investor%20attention%20to%20move%20away%20from%20Big%20Tech%20and%20toward%20companies%20integrating%20AI%20into%20their%20products%20and%20services%20to%20drive%20additional%20revenue%20growth%2C%20improve%20customer%20retention%2C%20and%20boost%20productivity%20and%20efficiency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20at%20this%20point%2C%20investors%20have%20three%20options.%20The%20first%20is%20to%20chase%20the%20crowd%20into%20a%20later%20phase%20of%20the%20AI%20trade%2C%20where%20bets%20are%20being%20made%20on%20which%20companies%20will%20successfully%20integrate%20AI%20for%20wider%20profit%20margins.%20Or%2C%20stay%20behind%20and%20look%20for%20sales%20on%20AI's%20picks%20and%20shovel%20stocks.%20Finally%2C%20they%20can%20choose%20to%20seek%20out%20more%20speculative%20opportunities%20in%20leading-edge%20sectors%20like%20robotics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEither%20way%2C%20the%20market%20could%20remain%20choppy%2C%20and%20volatility%20must%20be%20an%20accepted%20part%20of%20the%20trade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EStock%20picks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20software%20sector%20is%20a%20great%20place%20to%20look%20for%20AI%20bargains.%20Stocks%20in%20this%20corner%20were%20dumped%20in%20a%20flight%20to%20risk-off%20trades%2C%20including%20those%20with%20solid%20business%20models%20and%20recurring%20revenue%20growth%2C%20which%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20main%20point%3A%20if%20you're%20screening%20for%20names%20here%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20revenue%20growth%20above%20all%20else%20because%20the%20industry's%20perk%20is%20that%20it%20can%20grow%20fast%2C%20said%20Dan%20Romanoff%2C%20a%20senior%20equity%20research%20analyst%20for%20technology%20at%20Morningstar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20just%20draw%20a%20chart%20that%20compares%20software%20multiples%20versus%20revenue%20growth.%20And%20the%20higher%20the%20revenue%20growth%2C%20the%20higher%20the%20multiples%20will%20be%2C%20even%20if%20the%20company%20is%20losing%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Romanoff%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20looking%20at%20your%20portfolio%20holistically%2C%20tech%20is%20usually%20providing%20the%20most%20growth%20within%20your%20portfolio%2C%20and%20so%20you%20want%20to%20lean%20into%20the%20growth%20where%20you%20can%20get%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20key%20is%20to%20find%20the%20best%20growth%20story%2C%20he%20added.%20And%20the%20answer%20may%20not%20always%20be%20the%20company%20making%20the%20widest%20strides%20but%20rather%20the%20one%20that%20has%20shown%20sustainability%20in%20its%20revenue%20growth.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20a%20bump%20in%20revenue%20could%20be%20temporary%20due%20to%20a%20product%20release%2C%20which%20could%20fizzle%20out%20in%20the%20next%20quarter%2C%20he%20said.%20Knowing%20the%20difference%20is%20key%20to%20deciphering%20between%20a%20short-term%20trade%20and%20a%20long-term%20investment%20opportunity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithin%20software%2C%20stocks%20that%20are%20now%20well-priced%20include%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmsft-stock%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20of%20Thursday%2C%20it%20was%20down%20by%20almost%207%25%20this%20year.%20But%20it's%20still%20a%20harbor%20in%20a%20storm%20because%20of%20its%20blue-chip%20name%2C%20he%20noted.%20It%20has%20a%20monopoly%20in%20desktop%20operating%20systems%20with%20Windows.%20It%20has%20a%20near%20monopoly%20in%20productivity%20software%20in%20the%20office%20suites.%20Then%2C%20it%20piled%20on%20GenAI%20tools%2C%20which%20has%20catapulted%20it%20into%20a%20leadership%20spot%20in%20the%20AI%20race%2C%20Romanoff%20said.%20Its%20Azure%20is%20also%20a%20cloud%20provider%20in%20a%20three-horse%20race%20with%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%20and%20Google%20Cloud%20Platform.%20Romanoff%20believes%20cloud%20providers%20will%20be%20the%20real%20winners%20in%20GenAI%20because%20inference%20happens%20on%20these%20servers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fadbe-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdobe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20another%20software%20firm%20to%20bet%20on.%20It's%20not%20a%20pure%20AI%20play%2C%20which%20is%20positive%20because%20it%20means%20the%20company%20has%20a%20solid%2C%20long-running%20business.%20The%20stock%20is%20down%20by%20over%2010%25%20this%20year.%20It's%20being%20dumped%20because%20investors%20fear%20GenAI%20will%20take%20over.%20After%20all%2C%20GenAI%20is%20improving%20at%20creating%20images%20and%20could%20circumvent%20the%20need%20for%20Adobe's%20platform.%20But%20Romanoff%20believes%20Adobe's%20FireFly%2C%20which%20provides%20AI-based%20text-to-image%20and%20text-to-video%20options%2C%20will%20remain%20necessary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20still%20going%20to%20need%20tools%20to%20edit%20the%20content%20that%20is%20created%20by%20a%20generative%20AI%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20Romanoff%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20in%20advertising%20and%20creating%20a%20campaign%2C%20the%20images%20you%20create%20need%20to%20be%20very%20specifically%20edited%20to%20create%2C%20inform%2C%20and%20define%20the%20brand%20image%20you%20want.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20there's%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnow-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EServiceNow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It's%20a%20company%20that%20has%20successfully%20provided%20customer%20service%20and%20IT%20platforms.%20Its%20Q4%20revenue%20was%20up%20by%2021.34%25%20from%20last%20year.%20But%20the%20stock%20is%20down%20almost%2022%25%20this%20year.%20They%20have%20a%20solid%2C%20long-running%20business%20with%20only%20a%20small%20part%20of%20their%20revenue%20coming%20from%20GenAI%20offerings%2C%20Romanoff%20noted.%20Their%20annual%20recurring%20revenue%2C%20which%20is%20a%20key%20metric%20for%20software%20providers%2C%20has%20been%20on%20a%20solid%20growth%20trajectory%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you're%20curious%20about%20where%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Magnificent%207%20are%20trading%2C%20some%20are%20now%20well-priced%2C%20too.%20According%20to%20Morningstar's%20five-star%20rating%20system%2C%20which%20factors%20in%20volatility%20and%20uncertainty%2C%20these%20three%20names%20are%20now%20rated%20at%20four-stars%3A%20%3Cstrong%3EAmazon%20(AMZN)%2C%20Alphabet%20(GOOGL)%2C%20Meta%20(META)%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditional%20picks%20and%20shovel%20names%20that%20are%20now%20well%20priced%20and%20thus%20four-stars%20are%20%3Cstrong%3EASML%20(ASML)%2C%20Advanced%20Micro%20Devices%20(AMD)%2C%20and%20Marvell%20International%20(MRVL)%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20investors%20who%20want%20to%20make%20a%20more%20leading-edge%20bet%2C%20cheap%20or%20not%2C%20robotics%20is%20set%20to%20take%20off%20as%20automation%20integrates%20with%20AI.%20The%20two%20sectors%20combined%20now%20make%20up%201%25%20of%20global%20GDP.%20And%20that's%20expected%20to%20increase%20to%20a%20whopping%2035%25%20by%202040%2C%20according%20to%20VettaFi.%20Demand%20will%20come%20from%20manufacturing%2C%20healthcare%2C%20logistics%2C%20and%20agriculture%20end%20users.%20And%20that%20runway%20creates%20a%20trillion-dollar%20opportunity%20for%20investors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20betting%20in%20this%20sector%20can%20be%20trickier%20since%20a%20company's%20past%20fundamentals%20won't%20be%20the%20best%20measure%20of%20its%20future%20success.%20Here%2C%20Zeno%20Mercer%2C%20an%20investor%20and%20researcher%20in%20Deep%20Tech%20at%20VettaFi%2C%20says%20companies%20must%20be%20evaluated%20based%20on%20their%20contribution%20to%20relevant%20AI%20or%20robotics%20subsectors.%20They%20also%20need%20to%20be%20assessed%20on%20their%20technological%20leadership%2C%20their%20position%20within%20the%20market%2C%20such%20as%20who%20they%20are%20partnered%20with%2C%20and%20whether%20they're%20making%20strategic%20investments%20that%20will%20grow%20their%20presence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVettaFi's%20ROBO%20Global%20Robotics%20and%20Automation%20Index%20is%20one%20place%20to%20look%20for%20leading%20global%20companies%20in%20this%20arena.%20The%20Index's%20top%20holdings%20include%20names%20like%20%3Cstrong%3EHarmonic%20Drive%20Systems%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20makes%20precision%20control%20equipment%20for%20robots%3B%20%3Cstrong%3EFanuc%20Corp%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20robotics%20manufacturer%3B%20and%20%3Cstrong%3EGEA%20Group%20AG%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20an%20industrial%2C%20pharmaceutical%2C%20and%20chemical%20equipment%20manufacturer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-stocks-to-buy-while-cheaper-bear-market-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742546701000%