asurer%20of%20the%20Highway%20120%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%2C%20which%20represents%20businesses%20along%20the%20iconic%20thoroughfare%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPark%20advocates%20say%20the%20cuts%20could%20impact%20everything%20from%20visitor%20safety%20to%20bathroom%20maintenance%2C%20while%20business%20groups%20near%20the%20park%20say%20the%20uncertainty%20alone%20has%20taken%20a%20toll%20on%20their%20bookings%2C%20with%20tourists%20simply%20choosing%20to%20vacation%20elsewhere%20%E2%80%94%20to%20destinations%20untouched%20by%20DOGE-induced%20doubt%20and%20unpredictability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Protesters%20at%20Yosemite.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dc9f0ab8b41a9673fb4cef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222670%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDemonstrations%20against%20cuts%20to%20the%20National%20Park%20Service%20has%20taken%20place%20at%20Yosemite%20and%20other%20national%20parks%20around%20the%20US.%3Cp%3ELaure%20Andrillon%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22699c8a27-c821-41af-bd9d-5fe58959479f%5C%22%3ETourists%20are%20already%20rethinking%20their%20summer%20trips%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSummer%20bookings%20are%20way%20down%20over%20what%20we've%20ever%20seen%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lee%20Zimmerman%2C%20the%20co-owner%20of%20First%20Light%20Resorts%2C%20which%20owns%20or%20manages%20three%20resorts%20near%20Yosemite%3A%20Evergreen%20Lodge%2C%20Rush%20Creek%20Lodge%20and%20Spa%2C%20and%20Firefall%20Ranch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZimmerman%20told%20BI%20they%20are%20down%20thousands%20of%20booked%20rooms%20across%20the%20three%20properties%2C%20even%20though%20the%20main%20booking%20season%20for%20summer%20travel%20is%20typically%20January%20to%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20slashed%20thousands%20of%20jobs%20at%20the%20agencies%20that%20manage%20public%20lands%2C%20like%20the%20National%20Park%20Service%20and%20the%20US%20Forest%20Service.%20After%20a%20federal%20judge%20has%20ordered%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20reinstate%20fired%20probationary%20workers%2C%20NPS%20told%20BI%20it%20would%20work%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20order%20while%20the%20White%20House%20appeals.%20The%20National%20Park%20Conservation%20Association%20said%20Thursday%20NPS%20had%20authorized%20the%20rehiring%20of%20the%20nearly%201%2C000%20probationary%20employees%20whose%20jobs%20were%20terminated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20chaotic%20whiplash%20is%20no%20way%20to%20manage%20the%20Park%20Service%2C%20especially%20as%20they%20are%20welcoming%20millions%20of%20visitors%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Theresa%20Pierno%2C%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20park%20advocacy%20group%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20how%20that%20rehiring%20will%20play%20out%20or%20what%20could%20happen%20on%20appeal%2C%20so%20staffing%20levels%20at%20parks%20this%20summer%20remain%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%2C%20which%20oversees%20the%20US%20Forest%20Service%2C%20also%20told%20BI%20it%20was%20working%20on%20rehiring%20the%20fired%20probationary%20employees%20and%20said%20it%20intends%20%26quot%3Bto%20maintain%20access%20to%20recreation%20opportunities%20to%20the%20greatest%20degree%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20been%20other%20disruptions%2C%20too.%20At%20Yosemite%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20NPS%20last%20month%20suspended%20the%20timed-entry%20reservation%20system%2C%20which%20required%20visitors%20to%20reserve%20a%20set%20date%20and%20time%20to%20enter%20the%20park.%20Horn%20said%20not%20knowing%20whether%20there%20would%20be%20a%20reservation%20system%20or%20not%20has%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20people%20to%20plan%20trips%20%E2%80%94%20why%20book%20a%20hotel%20room%20when%20you%20can't%20be%20certain%20you'll%20even%20be%20able%20to%20get%20into%20the%20park%20on%20the%20days%20you're%20there%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20park%20service%20has%20still%20not%20said%20if%20the%20reservation%20system%20will%20be%20in%20place%20this%20summer%2C%20but%20Zimmerman%20said%20at%20this%20point%2C%20if%20the%20park%20decided%20to%20use%20one%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisaster%26quot%3B%20since%20it%20could%20disrupt%20trips%20that%20have%20already%20been%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Crowded%20summer%20beach%20with%20colorful%20umbrellas%2C%20Nauset%20Beach%2C%20Cape%20Cod%20National%20Seashore%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dca12cb8b41a9673fb4cff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223347%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Cape%20Cod%20National%20Seashore%20is%20a%20big%20draw%20for%20tourists%20during%20the%20summer.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Greim%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20on%20the%20east%20coast%2C%20Paul%20Niedzwiecki%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20Cape%20Cod%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20bookings%20of%20hotels%20and%20short-term%20lodging%20are%20currently%20down%20more%20than%205%25%20for%20the%20peak%20season%20of%20July%20and%20August%20in%20Cape%20Cod%2C%20a%20scenic%20peninsula%20in%20Massachusetts%20that's%20home%20to%20the%20Cape%20Cod%20National%20Seashore.%20If%20lodging%20rentals%20stay%20down%2C%20he%20said%2C%20that%20has%20a%20compounding%20effect%20on%20other%20local%20businesses%20like%20restaurants%20and%20outdoor%20recreation%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENiedzwiecki%20also%20expects%20to%20see%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanadians-boycott-us-travel-south-america-trump-tariff-trade-war-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edecline%20in%20visitors%20from%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%20the%20chamber%20has%20already%20heard%20from%20a%20number%20of%20recurring%20Canadian%20visitors%20who%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bvery%20direct%26quot%3B%20about%20not%20wanting%20to%20visit%20this%20year%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20they%20don't%20feel%20welcome%20given%20the%20state%20of%20national%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHorn%20said%20businesses%20in%20the%20Highway%20120%20corridor%20near%20Yosemite%20are%20also%20seeing%20fewer%20international%20visitors%20book%20summer%20trips%20to%20the%20area%2C%20something%20that%20is%20typically%20done%20well%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227797cdcc-39be-499f-815e-b84eb8c20b28%5C%22%3ENow%20might%20actually%20be%20a%20good%20time%20to%20visit%20a%20typically%20busy%20destination%20%E2%80%94%20with%20some%20precautions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Farrington%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20Yosemite%2FMariposa%20County%20Tourism%20Bureau%2C%20said%20they%20do%20not%20believe%20the%20visitor%20experience%20at%20Yosemite%20will%20be%20greatly%20impacted%20by%20the%20federal%20government%20change-ups.%20He%20noted%20that%20the%20park%20typically%20has%20nearly%20800%20full-time%20and%20seasonal%20staff%20in%20the%20summer%20and%20that%20about%2035%20positions%20have%20been%20cut%2C%20including%2010%20who%20were%20let%20go%20and%20around%2025%20who%20took%20the%20deferred%20resignation%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20important%20thing%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20be%20the%20park%20filling%20the%20around%20300%20seasonal%20positions.%20Though%20the%20administration's%20hiring%20freeze%20initially%20applied%20to%20seasonal%20workers%20at%20national%20parks%2C%20it%20later%20reversed%20course%20and%20said%20those%20hirings%20would%20go%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZimmerman%2C%20of%20the%20Yosemite%20resorts%2C%20also%20said%20that%20he%20is%20not%20concerned%20about%20the%20visitor%20experience%20in%20the%20park%20this%20year%2C%20and%20that%20now%20might%20actually%20be%20a%20good%20time%20to%20visit.%20Yosemite%2C%20like%20other%20popular%20national%20parks%2C%20has%20faced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-avoid-crowds-us-national-parks-tips-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eovercrowding%3C%2Fa%3E%20concerns%20in%20recent%20summers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Family%20at%20Yosemite%20poses%20with%20sequoia%20tree.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dc9f8463d72727e197d8d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMany%20national%20parks%20have%20dealt%20with%20overcrowding%20concerns%20in%20recent%20years.%3Cp%3EDAVID%20MCNEW%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20general%20confusion%20and%20concerns%20around%20staffing%2C%20reservations%2C%20and%20access%20to%20parks%20could%20be%20contributing%20to%20people%20staying%20away.%20%26quot%3BUncertainty%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20visitors%20to%20discern%20what's%20really%20going%20on%20and%20to%20commit%20to%20taking%20their%20vacation%20in%20the%20park%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20folks%20who%20do%20decide%20to%20visit%20public%20lands%20this%20year%2C%20it's%20still%20not%20clear%20what%20they%20will%20find.%20Park%20advocates%20have%20warned%20that%20if%20the%20staffing%20and%20funding%20cuts%20remain%2C%20summer%20visitors%20can%20expect%20a%20more%20restricted%2C%20if%20not%20more%20risky%2C%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVisitor%20centers%20will%20close%2C%20lines%20will%20grow%20longer%2C%20and%20basic%20maintenance%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20cleaning%20restrooms%20and%20facilities%20%E2%80%94%20will%20suffer%2C%26quot%3B%20Phil%20Francis%2C%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Coalition%20to%20Protect%20America's%20National%20Parks%20Executive%20Council%2C%20told%20BI%20of%20what%20could%20happen%20if%20parks%20are%20severely%20understaffed.%20%26quot%3BMillions%20of%20Americans%20who%20cherish%20their%20national%20parks%20may%20find%20them%20inaccessible%2C%20poorly%20maintained%2C%20or%20unsafe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarl%20Fisher%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Wyoming%20Outdoor%20Council%2C%20an%20environmental%20advocacy%20nonprofit%2C%20said%20visitors%20to%20places%20like%20Yellowstone%20National%20Park%20and%20Grand%20Teton%20National%20Park%20could%20see%20more%20trails%20and%20hiking%20areas%20being%20closed%20or%20having%20reduced%20hours%2C%20which%20could%20cut%20people's%20vacations%20short%2C%20he%20said.%20And%20if%20there%20are%20fewer%20workers%20to%20maintain%20them%2C%20the%20areas%20that%20do%20remain%20open%20may%20become%20more%20dangerous%20for%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20natural%2C%20wild%2C%20dynamic%20environments%2C%20and%20you%20can%20mess%20yourself%20up%20just%20crawling%20over%20and%20around%20deadfall.%20People%20can%20get%20lost%20because%2C%20well%2C%20they%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20find%20the%20trail%2C%26quot%3B%20Fisher%20told%20BI%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20poses%20a%20significant%20risk%20for%20inexperienced%20or%20first-time%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Park%20visitors%20sit%20on%20benches%20on%20the%20viewing%20platform%20awaiting%20the%20eruption%20of%20the%20Old%20Faithful%20cone%20geyser%20in%20Yellowstone%20National%20Park%2C%20Wyoming.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dca08fb8b41a9673fb4cfd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223467%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOutdoor%20advocates%20in%20Wyoming%20said%20NPS%20cuts%20could%20negatively%20impact%20trial%20access%20and%20facility%20maintenance%20at%20Yellowstone%20National%20Park.%3Cp%3ERon%20Buskirk%2FUCG%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22978dc3cc-52fe-4750-aca5-4b8fdaadc23f%5C%22%3ESmall%20businesses%20near%20national%20parks%20could%20feel%20the%20pinch%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20businesses%20like%20gear%20rental%20outfitters%20and%20guides%20rely%20on%20open%20and%20accessible%20parks%20to%20offer%20their%20services%2C%20said%20Grace%20Templeton%2C%20who%20works%20on%20community%20engagement%20projects%20at%20an%20outdoor%20recreation%20advocacy%20group%20called%20Wyoming%20Pathways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20trails%20are%20closed%20or%20poorly%20maintained%2C%20Templeton%20said%2C%20businesses%20that%20offer%20everything%20from%20mountain%20shuttle%20services%20to%20climbing%20guides%20to%20fishing%20expeditions%20could%20be%20upended.%20She's%20already%20heard%20from%20at%20least%20one%20business%20that's%20%26quot%3Bvery%20concerned%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20lifeline%20of%20its%20business%3A%20access%20to%20trails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETempleton%20also%20said%20that%20without%20federal%20funds%20for%20projects%20like%20trail%20development%2C%20local%20economies%20that%20rely%20on%20tourism%20could%20take%20a%20hit.%20For%20example%2C%20she%20said%2C%20her%20organization%20added%20a%20trail%20in%20the%20Thermopolis%20area%20of%20Wyoming%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20now%20they're%20getting%20tons%20of%20mountain%20bike%20tourism%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20%26quot%3Bit's%20very%20important%20for%20these%20trails%2C%20increased%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20residents%2C%20and%20drawing%20visitors%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHorn%2C%20of%20the%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20near%20Yosemite%2C%20said%20the%20cuts%20and%20uncertainty%20have%20made%20it%20hard%20for%20local%20businesses%20that%20rely%20on%20seasonal%20workers%20to%20know%20how%20many%20people%20to%20hire%20for%20the%20summer%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20them%20being%20under-%20or%20overstaffed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%20she%20said%20businesses%20near%20Yosemite%20are%20trying%20to%20get%20the%20message%20out%20that%20the%20national%20parks%20will%20be%20open%20this%20summer%2C%20but%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20information%20from%20the%20park%20service%20has%20made%20it%20unclear%20to%20many%20what%20exactly%20being%20open%20will%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt