ng%20room%20for%20the%20job%20hunt.%20But%20it's%20also%20a%20time%20to%20lament%20jobs%20that%20none%20are%20anticipating%20they'll%20actually%20get%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIdeally%2C%20I%20would%20return%20to%20my%20job.%20I%20just%20do%20not%20think%20that%20that's%20going%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20reinstated%20IRS%20worker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20reinstated%20Department%20of%20Energy%20worker%20said%20that%20they%20loved%20their%20job%20and%20their%20team%2C%20but%20they%20do%20expect%20to%20be%20let%20go%20again.%20They're%20%26quot%3Bnot%20at%20all%26quot%3B%20counting%20on%20actually%20staying.%20One%20reinstated%20NOAA%20worker%20said%2C%20emotionally%2C%20they've%20moved%20on.%20They%20still%20%26quot%3Badore%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20and%20think%20highly%20of%20it%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20too%20stressful%20to%20stay%20under%20the%20current%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20family%20to%20care%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20need%20to%20seek%20something%20else%20that%20is%20going%20to%20be%20not%20necessarily%20stable%2C%20because%20no%20job%20is%20really%20stable%2C%20but%20at%20least%20isn't%20going%20to%20treat%20me%20like%20dirt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20these%20reporters%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajkaplan%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejkaplan%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aaaltchek%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eaaltchek%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aasheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ansheidlower%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ensheidlower%40