ities%20are%20caught%20in%20the%20crosshairs%20of%20an%20intense%20crackdown%20by%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20facing%20unprecedented%20turmoil%20and%20uncertainty.%20What's%20behind%20this%20dramatic%20shift%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarack%20Obama%2C%20back%20when%20he%20was%20the%20US%20President%20and%20when%20intellectualism%20wasn't%20considered%20a%20liability%20in%20American%20politics%2C%20repeatedly%20stressed%20the%20need%20to%20invest%20in%20education%2C%20research%20and%20technology%20to%20keep%20the%20US%20ahead%20of%20rising%20powers%20like%20China%20and%20India.%20Yes%2C%20he%20singled%20out%20India%20and%20China%2C%20at%20least%20on%20two%20occasions%20that%20I%20can%20recall%2C%20as%20two%20potential%20threats%20to%20American%20innovation%20and%20research%20supremacy.%20His%20argument%20was%20that%20such%20investments%20were%20%E2%80%9Can%20essential%20down%20payment%20on%20our%20future%E2%80%9D%2C%20necessary%20for%20America%20to%20%E2%80%9Cout-educate%2C%20out-innovate%20and%20out-build%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%9D.%20He%20even%20went%20so%20far%20as%20to%20suggest%20that%20slashing%20funding%20for%20research%20and%20development%20could%20mean%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20great%20innovations%20of%20this%20century%E2%80%9D%20might%20not%20happen%20in%20America%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStarving%20Campuses%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%20today%2C%20and%20the%20Trump%20administration%20appears%20to%20have%20taken%20Obama's%20warning%20as%20a%20challenge.%20Instead%20of%20doubling%20down%20on%20America's%20intellectual%20and%20technological%20supremacy%2C%20it%20is%20using%20the%20Republican%20Party's%20ideological%20playbook%20to%20dismantle%20federal%20funding%20for%20research%2C%20treat%20professors%20as%20ideological%20enemies%20and%20wage%20war%20on%20the%20very%20institutions%20that%20made%20the%20US%20an%20academic%20superpower.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiberals%20call%20his%20action%20an%20assault%20on%20knowledge%3B%20conservatives%20call%20it%20a%20long-overdue%20reckoning.%20But%20if%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20India%20and%20China%20leapfrog%20ahead%20in%20scientific%20innovation%20while%20America%20bogs%20itself%20down%20in%20a%20culture%20war%20against%20universities%2C%20then%20soon%2C%20the%20administration's%20mission%20might%20even%20be%20accomplished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20academic%20sledgehammer%20fell%20on%20Columbia%20University%2C%20with%20the%20administration%20slashing%20%24400%20million%20in%20federal%20grants%E2%80%94ostensibly%20because%20the%20university%20had%20%E2%80%9Cfailed%20to%20protect%20American%20students%20and%20faculty%E2%80%9D%20from%20antisemitic%20harassment.%20Many%20Jewish%20students%20and%20teachers%20welcomed%20the%20action.%20But%20hundreds%20of%20other%20Jewish%20professors%2C%20scholars%20and%20students%20promptly%20signed%20a%20letter%20condemning%20the%20administration's%20move%2C%20making%20it%20clear%20that%20this%20wasn't%20about%20protecting%20Jewish%20students%20but%20about%20punishing%20academia%20for%20its%20perceived%20ideological%20sins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20the%20prestigious%20Johns%20Hopkins%20University%20learned%20that%20the%20administration%20was%20slashing%20a%20staggering%20%24800%20million%20in%20federal%20grants%2C%20primarily%20provided%20through%20USAID.%20A%20university%20press%20release%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWith%20the%20termination%20of%20more%20than%20%24800%20million%20in%20USAID%20grants%20at%20the%20university%2C%20Johns%20Hopkins%20has%20had%20to%20wind%20down%20much%20of%20its%20USAID%20grant-related%20activities%20in%20Baltimore%20and%20internationally.%20This%20has%20resulted%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20more%20than%202%2C200%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Assault%20Has%20Just%20Begun%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EColumbia%20and%20Johns%20Hopkins%20are%20just%20the%20beginning.%20The%20government%20has%20put%2060%20state%20and%20private%20colleges%20and%20universities%20under%20investigation%20for%20alleged%20antisemitic%20harassment%20related%20to%20pro-Palestinian%20protests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20has%20long%20dismissed%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20as%20a%20bloated%20relic%20polluted%20by%20liberal%20ideology.%20The%20Republicans%20believe%20the%20department%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20bureaucratic%20swamp%20in%20desperate%20need%20of%20draining.%20According%20to%20the%20US%20media%2C%20the%20President%20is%20now%20fully%20dismantling%20the%20department%20and%20has%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20to%20that%20effect.%20The%20Democratic%20Party%20argues%20that%20this%20is%20illegal%20and%20that%20dismantling%20the%20department%20would%20require%20Congress's%20approval.%20But%20legal%20hurdles%20seldom%20stand%20in%20the%20way%20of%20a%20culture%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Education's%20primary%20function%20isn't%20indoctrination%E2%80%94it's%20money.%20It%20distributes%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20federal%20funding%20to%20schools%20and%20universities%20and%20oversees%20the%20federal%20student%20loan%20system.%20Gutting%20it%20isn't%20just%20an%20ideological%20victory%E2%80%94it's%20a%20direct%20hit%20on%20low-income%20students%2C%20students%20of%20colour%2C%20and%20those%20with%20disabilities%2C%20who%20rely%20most%20on%20federal%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%20Indian%20Students%20In%20Headlines%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20has%20also%20launched%20a%20chilling%20crackdown%20on%20campus%20activism.%20Federal%20agents%20have%20detained%20several%20students%20who%20participated%20in%20last%20year's%20anti-Israeli%20or%20pro-Gaza%20protests.%20One%20Indian%20PhD%20student%2C%20Ranjani%20Srinivasan%2C%20had%20to%20use%20the%20government's%20self-deportation%20app%20to%20leave%20the%20country%2C%20while%20another%2C%20a%20postdoctoral%20fellow%20at%20Georgetown%20University%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20Monday.%20The%20administration%20has%20labelled%20Badar%20Khan%20Suri%20a%20threat%20to%20US%20foreign%20policy%2C%20citing%20alleged%20ties%20to%20Hamas%E2%80%94an%20accusation%20his%20lawyer%20calls%20absurd.%20A%20rarely%20used%20immigration%20law%20is%20being%20used%20to%20fast-track%20his%20deportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20started%20with%20the%20arrest%20of%20Mahmoud%20Khalil%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20refugee%20whose%20green%20card%20was%20revoked%20over%20his%20involvement%20in%20Columbia%20University%20protests.%20It%20sent%20a%20chill%20across%20campuses%20nationwide.%20Columbia%20has%2024%2C000%20international%20students%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20unsure%20whether%20they%20would%20be%20allowed%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20country.%20Students%20are%20now%20forced%20to%20second-guess%20whether%20exercising%20their%20constitutionally%20protected%20right%20to%20free%20speech%20is%20worth%20the%20risk.%20The%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20wasted%20no%20time%20in%20making%20an%20example%20out%20of%20Khalil%2C%20after%20all%2C%20following%20up%20with%20the%20arrest%20of%20Leqaa%20Kordia%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20student%20from%20the%20West%20Bank.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20has%20promised%20to%20strip%20visas%20and%20green%20cards%20from%20what%20he%20called%20%E2%80%9CHamas%20supporters%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20convenient%20catch-all%20for%20anyone%20who%20dares%20to%20advocate%20for%20Palestinian%20rights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERemember%20Mao's%20China%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat's%20happening%20in%20America%20today%20bears%20eerie%20similarities%20to%20China's%20Cultural%20Revolution%2C%20where%20Mao%20Zedong%20purged%20academia%2C%20shut%20down%20universities%20and%20crushed%20intellectual%20freedom%20in%20his%20quest%20to%20%E2%80%9Crevolutionise%E2%80%9D%20the%20country.%20The%20consequences%20of%20Trump's%20assault%20on%20universities%20are%20monumental.%20It%20threatens%20to%20end%20US%20supremacy%20in%20research%20and%20quality%20education.%20Indian-origin%20journalist%20and%20political%20commentator%20Fareed%20Zakaria%20recently%20noted%20that%20while%20America%20is%20copying%20Mao's%20assault%20on%20universities%2C%20China%20is%20adopting%20the%20best%20of%20what%20the%20US%20offers%E2%80%94world-class%20education%2C%20cutting-edge%20research%20and%20technological%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20see%20Trump's%20actions%20as%20a%20war%20against%20liberalism%20and%20elitism.%20But%20dig%20deeper%20and%20the%20President's%20motives%20make%20political%20sense.%20In%20the%202020%20election%2C%2065%25%20of%20non-college%20voters%20backed%20Trump%2C%20while%2061%25%20of%20university-educated%20voters%20went%20for%20Joe%20Biden.%20The%202024%20election%20results%20show%20a%20similar%20pattern.%20It%20is%20well%20established%20that%20Trump%20supporters%20and%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Great%20Again%26quot%3B%20(MAGA)%20activists%20distrust%20universities%2C%20believing%20them%20to%20be%20ideological%20breeding%20grounds%20for%20liberals%20and%20leftists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20explains%20why%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%2C%20back%20when%20he%20was%20a%20senator%20in%202021%2C%20chillingly%20declared%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20honestly%20and%20aggressively%20attack%20universities%20in%20this%20country.%20The%20professors%20are%20the%20enemy.%E2%80%9D%20Trump%20and%20his%20staunch%20supporters%20also%20despise%20diversity%20and%20inclusion%20programmes.%20Universities%20that%20promote%20diversity%2C%20equity%20and%20inclusion%20(DEI)%20programmes%20have%20seen%20their%20funding%20getting%20slashed.%20Under%20government%20pressure%2C%20initiatives%20celebrating%20inclusion%20have%20been%20dismantled%2C%20while%20diversity%20itself%20is%20being%20reframed%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20American%20Self-Sabotage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20stake%20is%20not%20just%20freedom%20of%20speech%2C%20disgruntled%20professors%20or%20campus%20protests%E2%80%94it's%20America's%20entire%20supremacy%20in%20research%20and%20innovation.%20Federal%20funding%20cuts%20are%20jeopardising%20groundbreaking%20research%20on%20cancer%2C%20vaccines%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20other%20scientific%20advancements%20that%20have%20historically%20kept%20the%20US%20ahead%20of%20the%20world.%20But%20now%2C%20America's%20%26quot%3Bwar%20on%20knowledge%26quot%3B%20might%20just%20ensure%20that%20if%20the%20next%20great%20scientific%20breakthrough%20happens%2C%20it%20likely%20won't%20be%20in%20an%20American%20lab%E2%80%94it'll%20be%20in%20China%20or%20even%20India.%20While%20India's%20budget%20on%20technology%2C%20research%20and%20higher%20education%20has%20ballooned%20over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20decades%2C%20Beijing%20too%20has%20been%20pouring%20billions%20into%20AI%2C%20biotechnology%2C%20and%20quantum%20computing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20get%20worse%20as%20the%20brain%20drain%20starts%20soon.%20Why%20would%20brilliant%20minds%20stay%20in%20a%20country%20where%20academic%20freedom%20is%20on%20life%20support%20and%20research%20funding%20is%20being%20redirected%20to%20serve%20political%20agendas%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20it%20will%20affect%20the%20US%20economy%20too.%20Tech%20companies%2C%20medical%20research%20and%20engineering%20firms%20all%20rely%20on%20the%20steady%20pipeline%20of%20talent%20and%20ideas%20churned%20out%20by%20universities.%20When%20these%20institutions%20crumble%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20political%20interference%2C%20expect%20the%20economy%20to%20follow%20suit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Syed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20media)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742541120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fenpluf9o_donald-trump_625x300_03_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ftrumps-war-on-universities-has-eerie-resemblance-to-60s-china-7974597%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Trump%20administration%2C%20in%20its%20all-out%20assault%20on%20universities%2C%20has%20already%20slashed%20federal%20grants%20worth%20%24800%20million%20and%20%24400%20million%20for%20Johns%20Hopkins%20and%20Columbia%2C%20respectively.%20But%20this%20is%20just%20the%20beginning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ftrumps-war-on-universities-has-eerie-resemblance-to-60s-china-7974597%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20rolls%20out%20AI-powered%20'smart%20search'%20feature%20in%20Gmail%3A%20What's%20new%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742541113000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fgoogle-rolls-out-ai-powered-smart-search-feature-in-gmail-what-s-new-125032100394_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20search%20option%20is%20currently%20rolling%20out%20for%20users%20with%20personal%20Google%20accounts%20and%20is%20available%20on%20both%20the%20web%20and%20the%20official%20Gmail%20app%20for%20Android%20and%20iOS%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fgoogle-rolls-out-ai-powered-smart-search-feature-in-gmail-what-s-new-125032100394_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Nitish%20not%20stable%2C%20make%20his%20son%20Bihar%20CM'%3A%20Rabri%20Devi%20over%20national%20anthem%20incident%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A174254052600