0tribe%20is%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20indigenous%20communities%20that%20is%20exceptionally%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F326801%2Fvedhapriya-ganesan-snake-rescuer-wildlife-conservationist-pet-stylist-chennai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20adept%20at%20handling%20snakes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20expertise%20in%20reptiles%20and%20venom%20collection%20acumen%20cast%20them%20into%20the%20spotlight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20also%20made%20them%20victim%20to%20certain%20scams.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20Irula%20tribe%20were%20deceived%20into%20procuring%20snake%20skins%20%E2%80%94%20lucrative%20for%20the%20fashion%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20that%20were%20sold%20illegally.%20The%20Indian%20Wildlife%20Protection%20Act%20(1972)%20came%20as%20a%20relief%20to%20this%20illicit%20trade.%20But%20this%20also%20put%20a%20damper%20on%20the%20tribe%E2%80%99s%20livelihood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERespite%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20help%20from%20herpetologist%20Romulus%20Whitaker%2C%20who%20aided%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20Irula%20Snake%20Catchers%20Industrial%20Cooperative%20Society%20(ISCICS)%20in%201978.%20The%20cooperative%20has%20risen%20to%20the%20ranks%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20producer%20of%20snake%20venom.%20But%20venom%20collection%20is%20just%20a%20part%20of%20the%20collective%E2%80%99s%20overarching%20aim%20of%20sustainable%20employment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajendra%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Irula%20tribe%2C%20elaborated%20on%20the%20process%20of%20venom%20tapping.%C2%A0%20Once%20tracked%20down%2C%20the%20venomous%20snakes%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%2