0of%20unaccounted%20cash%20was%20found%20in%20his%20official%20bungalow%20in%20Delhi%20last%20week%2C%20during%20Holi%20vacations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20was%20discovered%20after%20a%20fire%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20building%20and%20family%20members%20of%20the%20judge%20-%20who%20was%20not%20in%20the%20city%20at%20the%20time%20-%20called%20emergency%20services%2C%20who%20then%20called%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20informed%20of%20the%20matter%20as%20it%20travelled%20up%20through%20official%20channels%2C%20the%20Collegium%2C%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20decided%20to%20transfer%20Justice%20Verma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Verma%20has%20not%20yet%20responded%20to%20the%20recovery%20of%20the%20cash%20and%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20did%20not%20hold%20court%20today.%20Sources%20told%20PTI%20he%20had%20gone%20%26quot%3Bon%20leave%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20took%20a%20very%20serious%20view%20of%20the%20discovery%20of%20the%20cash%20and%20the%20five-member%20Collegium%20concurred%2C%20agreeing%20unanimously%20on%20Justice%20Verma's%20transfer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20sources%20also%20said%20some%20members%20felt%20stricter%20action%20was%20required%20to%20avoid%20tarnishing%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20judiciary%2C%20which%20would%20have%20serious%20consequences%20on%20its%20ability%20to%20deliver%20justice%20to%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%2C%20therefore%2C%20also%20talk%20of%20Justice%20Verma%20being%20asked%20to%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20he%20refuse%20to%20do%20so%2C%20some%20of%20the%20Collegium%20felt%2C%20an%20internal%20inquiry%20could%20be%20initiated%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%3B%20this%20would%20be%20the%20first%20step%20in%20his%20being%20removed%20by%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Everyone%20Demoralised'%3A%20Delhi%20Chief%20Justice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20DK%20Upadhyaya%2C%20responding%20to%20senior%20advocate%20Arun%20Bhardwaj%20mentioning%20this%20matter%20in%20court%2C%20admitted%20that%20everyone%20had%20been%20left%20%26quot%3Bshaken%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday's%20incident%20has%20pained%20many%20of%20us.%20Please%20take%20some%20steps%20on%20the%20administrative%20side%20so%20these%20incidents%20do%20not%20happen%20in%20future%20and%20the%20judicial%20system%20is%20maintained...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhardwaj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Can%20High%20Court%20Judges%20Be%20Removed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201999%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20laid%20down%20guidelines%20to%20deal%20with%20allegations%20of%20corruption%2C%20wrongdoing%2C%20and%20judicial%20irregularity%20against%20judges%20of%20the%20Constitutional%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20these%20guidelines%2C%20on%20receiving%20a%20complaint%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20will%20first%20seek%20a%20reply%20from%20the%20judge%20concerned.%20If%20he%20is%20dissatisfied%20with%20the%20answer%2C%20or%20believes%20the%20matter%20requires%20further%20investigation%2C%20he%20will%20form%20an%20internal%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20committee%20will%20consist%20of%20one%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20and%20two%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20committee%20submits%20a%20report%20and%20if%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20is%20then%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20the%20alleged%20misconduct%20is%20of%20a%20grave%20nature%20requiring%20removal%2C%20he%20will%20ask%20the%20judge%20to%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20judge%20were%20to%20refuse%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20will%20then%20write%20to%20the%20government%20to%20initiate%20proceedings%20for%20his%2Fher%20removal%20by%20Parliament%2C%20under%20Article%20124(4)%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Action%20Needed'%3A%20Kapil%20Sibal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%C2%A0senior%20advocate%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Kapil%20Sibal%20has%20urged%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20%26quot%3Bstart%20looking%20at%20how%20the%20appointment%20process%20(to%20nominate%20judges)%20takes%20place%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Delhi%20%7C%20On%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Collegium%20recommending%20transfer%20of%20Justice%20Yashwant%20Varma%20of%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20to%20his%20parent%20High%20Court%20in%20Allahabad%20after%20an%20adverse%20report%20against%20him%2C%20Senior%20advocate%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Kapil%20Sibal%20says%2C%20%26quot%3B...The%20issue%20of%20corruption%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FhPQPqeT57t%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FhPQPqeT57t%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1902947483204063534%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2021%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20issue%20of%20corruption%20within%20the%20judiciary%20is%20very%20serious...%20this%20is%20not%20something%20articulated%20by%20senior%20councils%20and%20lawyers%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20It%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20appointment%20process%20should%20be%20more%20transparent%20and%20carefully%20done...Corruption%20is%20a%20very%20serious%20issue%20and%2C%20despite%20what%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20said%2C%20corruption%20has%20increased...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20