a%20week%20after%20he%20had%20returned%20from%20abroad%20to%20celebrate%20his%20daughter's%20birthday.%20His%20wife%20Muskaan%20Rastogi%20and%20friend%20Sahil%20Shukla%2C%20with%20whom%20she%20had%20an%20extramarital%20affair%2C%20were%20later%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20top%20police%20officer%20overseeing%20the%20probe%20has%20answered%2010%20questions%20after%20the%20grisly%20murder%20sparked%20speculation%20over%20black%20magic%2C%20Muskaan's%20alcohol%20addiction%2C%20and%20her%20alleged%20aspiration%20to%20make%20it%20big%20in%20Bollywood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyush%20Vikram%20Singh%2C%20the%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Meerut%20City%20said%20the%20police%20are%20still%20investigating%20the%20motive%20and%20shared%20the%20evidence%20so%20far%20collected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20said%20Muskaan%20and%20Sahil%20had%20confessed%20to%20killing%20Saurabh.%20They%20sealed%20the%20victim's%20body%20in%20a%20drum%20with%20cement%20and%20fled%20to%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20When%20they%20returned%20two%20days%20later%2C%20they%20were%20taken%20into%20custody.%20They%20admitted%20their%20crime%20during%20questioning.%20The%20weapon%20used%20in%20the%20murder%20has%20also%20been%20recovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Extramarital%20Affair%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskaan%20and%20Saurabh%20had%20a%20love%20marriage%20in%202016%2C%20but%20their%20joy%20was%20short-lived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20Saurabh%20learnt%20about%20Muskaan's%20affair%20back%20in%202021.%20Their%20landlord%20had%20informed%20him%20after%20spotting%20Muskaan%20and%20Sahil%20in%20an%20%26quot%3Bobjectionable%26quot%3B%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20her%20interrogation%2C%20Muskaan%20said%20that%20she%20was%20in%20an%20illicit%20relationship%20with%20Sahil%20since%202019.%20Saurabh%20was%20aware%20of%20this%20and%20had%20filed%20for%20divorce%20in%202021.%20But%20his%20family%20had%20convinced%20him%20to%20stay%20with%20his%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20SP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskaan%20has%20claimed%20that%20Sahil%20was%20a%20liquor%20addict%2C%20which%20often%20led%20to%20quarrels%20between%20them.%20Sahil%20was%20also%20in%20a%20financial%20crunch%20and%20her%20family%20used%20to%20bear%20his%20expenses%2C%20including%20rent%2C%20she%20told%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Earlier%20Attempt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20family%20had%20earlier%20accused%20Sahil%20of%20getting%20her%20addicted%20to%20drugs.%20The%20police%20have%20confirmed%20that%20they%20consumed%20liquor%20as%20frequently%20as%20they%20met%2C%20but%20Muskaan%20claimed%20she%20used%20to%20drink%20even%20before%20she%20met%20Sahil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%202023%2C%20Saurabh%20worked%20at%20a%20bakery%20in%20London.%20He%20came%20back%20to%20India%20on%20February%2024.%20The%20accused%20tried%20to%20kill%20him%20on%20February%2025%20but%20could%20not%20succeed.%20They%20finally%20executed%20their%20plan%20on%20March%203%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20that%20two%20teams%20have%20been%20formed%20to%20probe%20the%20murder.%20The%20police%20have%20identified%20the%20shop%20from%20where%20they%20bought%20the%20drum%20and%20other%20materials%20allegedly%20used%20in%20the%20murder%2C%20and%20the%20shopkeeper%20has%20been%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20said%20a%20police%20team%20would%20leave%20for%20Shimla%20soon%20to%20collect%20more%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20collecting%20information%20about%20the%20places%20where%20they%20went%20outside%20Shimla%2C%20their%20phones%20have%20been%20sent%20for%20forensic%20test...so%20that%20we%20can%20file%20a%20chargesheet%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20and%20give%20them%20the%20harshest%20punishment%20through%20the%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlack%20Magic%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20severed%20