t%20for%20her%20parents'%20house.%20But%20finding%20a%20foul%20smell%2C%20they%20suspected%20something%20amiss%20and%20called%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskaan%20confessed%20to%20her%20mother%2C%20who%20reported%20her%20to%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20the%20victim's%20daughter%20knew%20about%20her%20father's%20death%2C%20his%20mother%20Renu%20Devi%20said%20the%20six-year-old%20girl%20had%20been%20telling%20neighbours%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeerut-saurabh-rajput-murder-cement-murder-papa-drum-mein-hain-merchant-navy-officers-daughter-6-told-neighbours-7965407%5C%22%3EPapa%20is%20in%20the%20drum%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BShe%20must%20have%20seen%20something.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742537580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F4i142cq_meerut-cement-murder_625x300_19_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcops-share-key-details-on-meerut-murder-black-magic-money-transfers-7973604%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20police%20in%20Meerut%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20have%20shared%20their%20key%20findings%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20former%20Merchant%20Navy%20officer%20allegedly%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20her%20lover.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcops-share-key-details-on-meerut-murder-black-magic-money-transfers-7973604%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cash%20found%20at%20judge's%20house%20after%20fire%3A%20Who%20is%20Justice%20Yashwant%20Varma%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742537349000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fjustice-yashwant-varma-transfer-cash-fire-delhi-high-court-125032100311_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Collegium%20has%20ordered%20the%20immed