20has%20retaken%20the%20Republican%20Palace%20in%20Khartoum%2C%20the%20last%20heavily%20guarded%20bastion%20of%20rival%20paramilitary%20forces%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20after%20nearly%20two%20years%20of%20fighting.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsudans-military-says-it-has-seized-control-of-presidential-palace-13332962%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsudans-military-says-it-has-seized-control-of-presidential-palace-13332962%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsudans-military-says-it-has-seized-control-of-presidential-palace-13332962%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Bhutan%3A%20A%20Priapic%20Obsession%20And%20Real%20Luxury%20In%20A%20300-Year-Old%20Farmhouse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChimmi%2C%20the%20restaurant%20manager%20at%20the%20Aman%2C%20Thimphu%2C%20noticed%20me%20flinching%20with%20pain%20during%20the%20breakfast%20service.%20A%20catch%20in%20my%20neck%E2%80%94probably%20from%20a%20faulty%20sleeping%20position.%20%E2%80%9CLet%20me%20organise%20a%20therapist%20at%20the%20spa%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20whispered.%20Even%20slight%20distress%2C%20on%20the%20road%2C%20registers%20intensely%3B%20you%20miss%20home%20more%2C%20wondering%20why%20you%20left%20familiar%20turf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20restaurant%2C%20framed%20views%20of%20pine-cloaked%20mountains%3B%20a%20sharp%20blue%20sky%2C%20cloudless.%20Boulders%20across%20the%20ridge%20like%20characters%20out%20of%20Bhutanese%20legends%2C%20ancient%20forms%20steeped%20in%20myth.%20A%20great%20spring%20coursing%20through%20the%20valley%20was%20audible%20in%20the%20Aman's%20comforting%20and%20beautiful%20spa%2C%20where%20Pema%E2%80%94the%20considerate%20spa%20supervisor%E2%80%94tried%20to%20ease%20the%20niggle%20in%20my%20neck%20and%20shoulder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHappiness%20And%20Compassion%20To%20Counter%20Dukkha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFeted%20as%20the%20happiest%20country%20in%20the%20world%2C%20Bhutan%20is%20also%20home%20to%20some%20of%20the%20kindest%20people.%20On%20previous%20trips%2C%20I've%20encountered%20a%20specific%20kind%20of%20compassion%20here%2C%20without%20a%20vein%20of%20pity%3B%20it%20races%20to%20counter%20the%20experience%20of%20%3Cem%3Edukkha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(it%20might%20also%20be%20that%20the%20Aman%20selects%20staff%20with%20a%20genius%20for%20thoughtfulness).%20Chimmi%20and%20Pema%2C%20with%20their%20motive-free%20desire%20to%20help%2C%20begged%20the%20question%3A%20are%20happiness%20and%20compassion%20linked%20with%20some%20subtle%20thread%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Amankora%20swaps%20opulence%20for%20intimacy.%20Photo%3A%20Author%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Amankora%20swaps%20opulence%20for%20intimacy.%20Photo%3A%20Author%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fmvg0jlmo_amankora-bhutan_625x300_21_March_25.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAmankora%20in%20Bhutan%20swaps%20opulence%20for%20intimacy.%20Photo%3A%20Author%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20developing%20world%20prizes%20growth%20in%20terms%20of%20development%E2%80%94malls%2C%20freeways.%20Perhaps%20this%20metric%20of%20development%2C%20inherited%20from%20the%20West%2C%20is%20entirely%20broken.%20Psychological%20well-being%2C%20environmental%20conservation%20(Bhutan%20is%20carbon-negative)%2C%20cultural%20preservation%20(the%20temples%20preserve%20exquisite%20iconography)%E2%80%94maybe%20these%20should%20be%20real%20markers%20of%20progress.%20After%20all%2C%20in%20countries%20with%20extreme%20development%2C%20like%20America%2C%20there%20are%20mental%20health%20epidemics%20-%20and%20political%20leaders%20best%20described%20as%20borderline%20insane%20despots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Priapic%20Obsession%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20penises%20everywhere%E2%80%94bold%2C%20stunning%20hard-ons.%20Painted%20on%20walls.%20As%20plastic%20keychains.%20Wooden%20boners%20nailed%20above%20doorways.%20Signs%20of%20fertility%20and%20symbols%20of%20divine%20protection%2C%20Bhutan's%20priapic%20obsession%20transcends%20anatomy%20and%20is%20anchored%20in%20spirituality.%20The%2015th-century%20Buddhist%20saint%2C%20Drukpa%20Kunley%E2%80%94affectionately%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BDivine%20Madman%26quot%3B%E2%80%94championed%20these%20symbols%2C%20enmeshing%20eroticism%20with%20enlightenment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Karma%20Choden's%20%3Cem%3EPhallus%3A%20Crazy%20Wisdom%20from%20Bhutan%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Marc%20Domsky's%20photographic%20journey%2C%20%3Cem%3EPhallus%20Through%20Bhutan%3A%20Journey%20of%20the%20Magic%20Thunderbolt%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20we%20read%E2%80%94along%20with%20some%20far-out%20visual%20evidence%E2%80%94how%20they%20are%20talismans%20against%20malevolence%2C%20markers%20of%20prosperity%2C%20boons%20for%20progeny%2C%20reflecting%20a%20culture%20where%20the%20sacred%20and%20sacrilegious%20integrate%20fearlessly.%20I%20got%20a%20large%20wooden%20one%20for%20an%20aunty%20of%20mine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20Move%20Is%20To%20Risk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20drive%20out%20to%20Punakha%2C%20the%20neck%20remains%20in%20agony.%20Mentally%2C%20I%20take%20stock%20of%20other%20writers%20who%20endured%20far%20worse%20fates%20on%20the%20road.%20Bruce%20Chatwin%2C%20fevered%20and%20frail%20in%20Patagonia%2C%20his%20body%20betraying%20him%20even%20as%20the%20landscape%20turned%20into%20his%20muse.%20Bill%20Bryson%2C%20sun-scorched%20in%20Australia%2C%20learned%20how%20heat%20tasers%20humour%20to%20stoicism.%20And%20Rolf%20Potts%2C%20wandering%20through%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20saw%20in%20food%20poisoning%20not%20an%20enemy%20but%20an%20initiation%E2%80%94diarrhoea%20as%20portal%20to%20enlightenment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20move%20is%20to%20risk%3B%20all%20risk%20entails%20surrender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fmdqtjs3o_bhutan-travelogue-sds_625x300_21_March_25.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20landscape%20changed%20as%20we%20drove%20through%20a%20botanical%20park.%20Cherry%20blossoms%20dusted%20the%20streets%20with%20pale%20pink%20confetti.%20Jacarandas%2C%20a%20great%20riot%20of%20purple%20against%20the%20stern%20green%20of%20the%20hills.%20Along%20riverbanks%2C%20near%20monasteries%20where%20prayer%20wheels%20spun%20in%20unending%20devotion%2C%20rhododendrons%20erupted%20in%20hues%20of%20red%20and%20orange.%20White%20prayer%20flags%2C%20installed%20to%20honour%20the%20dead%2C%20were%20reminders%20of%20mortality.%20A%20pain%20in%20the%20neck%20humbled%20me.%20I%20recalled%20the%20Lord%20in%20one%20breath%E2%80%94although%20I%20was%20never%20so%20elevated%20as%20to%20withhold%20expletives%20at%20the%20Neck%20Pain%20Demons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20drive%20to%20Punakha%2C%20my%20driver%20Namgay%20Tshering%20and%20my%20guide%2C%20Kuenley%20Dorjee%2C%20both%20dispatched%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Tourism%2C%20were%20ambassadors%20of%20Bhutan's%20savant%20grace.%20The%20driver%20slowed%20the%20car%20to%20soothe%20my%20condition.%20Kuenley%20got%20me%20a%20hot%20water%20bag%20with%20a%20print%20of%20teddy%20bears.%20Later%20we%20would%20go%20to%20the%20local%20market%20to%20buy%20offering%20bowls%20and%20saffron%20and%20camphor.%20At%20every%20step%2C%20their%20discreet%20concern%20was%20blessing%20in%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Micro-resort%20From%20Before%20Micro-resorts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicro%20resorts%2C%20blending%20design-forward%20aesthetics%20with%20sustainability%2C%20have%20redefined%20travel%20experience%2C%20swapping%20opulence%20for%20intimacy.%20In%20Mexico%2C%20Hotelito%20Desconocido%20embraced%20an%20off-grid%20ethos%2C%20its%20palafitte-style%20rooms%20floating%20over%20an%20estuary.%20In%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20Las%20Catalinas%2C%20a%20walkable%2C%20car-free%20village%20conceived%20by%20Douglas%20Duany%2C%20integrates%20with%20its%20lush%20surroundings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Amankora%20Punakha%20Lodge.%20Photo%3A%20Amankora%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Amankora%20Punakha%20Lodge.%20Photo%3A%20Amankora%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F2nhm9poo_amankora-microresort_625x300_21_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAmankora%20Punakha%20Lodge.%20Photo%3A%20Amankora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong%20before%20micro-resorts%20became%20TikTok's%20biggest%20travel%20trend%2C%20there%20was%20the%20ten-room%E2%80%94though%20since%20slightly%20expanded%E2%80%94Amankora%20Punakha%20Lodge%2C%20designed%20by%20the%20late%20Kerry%20Hill%2C%20set%20in%20a%20300-year-old%20Bhutanese%20farmhouse%20built%20by%20a%20former%20Je%20Khenpo%20(chief%20abbot).%20The%20resort%2C%20with%20pared-down%20interiors%20and%20an%20inviting%20autumnal%20palette%2C%20is%20among%20my%20favourite%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20sublime%20infinity%20pool%20overlooks%20fields%20and%20hills%3B%20there%20is%20a%20meditation%20room%20with%20a%20heart-stilling%20altar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPain%2C%20And%20The%20Palace%20Of%20Great%20Happiness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20here%2C%20I%20head%20to%20the%20Punakha%20Dzong%20(formally%3A%20Pungthang%20Dewachen%20Phodrang%2C%20meaning%20%E2%80%9CPalace%20of%20Great%20Happiness%E2%80%9D).%20Each%20spring%2C%20the%20majestic%20Punakha%20Dzong%2C%20Bhutan's%20former%20capital%2C%20turns%20into%20a%20stage%20for%20Punakha%20Tshechu%2C%20a%20lunar%20spring%20festival.%20The%20narrow%20road%20is%20lined%20with%20street%20food%20stalls%20and%20a%20hodgepodge%20of%20local%20crafts.%20Locals%20are%20dressed%20in%20their%20finery%20as%20we%20walk%20over%20a%20bridge%3B%20below%2C%20in%20the%20unifying%20currents%20of%20Pho%20Chhu%20and%20Mo%20Chhu%20rivers%2C%20large%20black%20fish%20float%20serenely.%20The%20scent%20of%20juniper%20incense%20is%20a%20rumour%20of%20divine%20presences.%20The%20crowds%20are%20orderly%2C%20reverential%2C%20polite%20to%20a%20fault%3B%20several%20devotees%20ducked%20so%20I%20might%20enjoy%20a%20clearer%20view.%20If%20such%20a%20gathering%20was%20in%20India%2C%20a%20stampede%20was%20a%20statistical%20possibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20courtyard%2C%20monks%20and%20performers%20don%20masks%20and%20silk%20robes%20before%20racing%20down%20a%20long%20stone%20staircase%2C%20their%20dramatic%20movements%20echoing%20those%20of%20ancient%20warriors.%20Behind%20me%2C%20in%20the%20distance%2C%20more%20battle%20cries%2C%20men%20on%20horses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Punakha%20Dzong%20(formally%3A%20Pungthang%20Dewachen%20Phodrang%2C%20meaning%20%E2%80%9CPalace%20of%20Great%20Happiness%E2%80%9D).%20Photo%3A%20Amankora%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Punakha%20Dzong%20(formally%3A%20Pungthang%20Dewachen%20Phodrang%2C%20meaning%20%E2%80%9CPalace%20of%20Great%20Happiness%E2%80%9D).%20Photo%3A%20Amankora%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fkoqm38bo_punakha-dzong_625x300_21_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPunakha%20Dzong%20(formally%3A%20Pungthang%20Dewachen%20Phodrang%2C%20meaning%20%E2%80%9CPalace%20of%20Great%20Happiness%E2%80%9D).%20Photo%3A%20Amankora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20magic%20hours%20come%20alive%20with%20faith%20and%20history.%20Dazzled%20by%20a%20retelling%20of%20ancient%20legends%2C%20I%20feel%20briefly%20free%20of%20the%20pain.%20I%20have%20entered%20the%20narrative%E2%80%94I%20am%20in%20the%20myth%2C%20which%20is%20to%20say%3A%20I%20am%20no%20longer%20in%20the%20first%20person.%20Travel%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20is%20not%20about%20miles%20covered%20but%20how%20the%20world%E2%80%94with%20heat%20o