ed%20by%20CNN%2C%20said%20that%20initiating%20the%20legal%20process%20would%20help%20them%20grieve%20and%20address%20related%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20believe%20their%20daughter%20drowned%20and%20no%20criminal%20evidence%20has%20been%20found%20so%20they%20urged%20authorities%20to%20%26quot%3Bproceed%20with%20the%20legal%20declaration%20of%20her%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheriff%20Mike%20Chapman%20said%20that%20while%20investigators%20believe%20Ms%20Konanki%20drowned%2C%20her%20death%20has%20not%20been%20officially%20confirmed%2C%20and%20the%20case%20remains%20open.%20Authorities%20in%20the%20Dominican%20Republic%20are%20continuing%20their%20investigation%2C%20and%20legal%20experts%20note%20that%20declaring%20someone%20dead%20without%20a%20body%20is%20a%20complex%20process%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20attorney%20Julio%20Cury%2C%20such%20a%20declaration%20would%20require%20special%20approval%20from%20Congress%20or%20the%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Loudoun%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%20has%20offered%20assistance%20to%20the%20family%20in%20navigating%20the%20process%2C%20including%20judicial%20procedures%20if%20necessary.%20Personal%20injury%20and%20criminal%20defence%20attorney%20Phillip%20DiLucente%20explained%20that%20the%20family's%20request%20is%20likely%20driven%20by%20a%20need%20for%20closure.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20parental%20position%2C%20they%20want%20to%20honour%20their%20child%20and%20have%20it%20be%20respected%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20legal%20declaration%20of%20death%20would%20also%20allow%20the%20family%20to%20settle%20financial%20matters%2C%20such%20as%20college%20savings%20plans%20and%20insurance%20policies.%20Until%20a%20death%20certificate%20is%20issued%2C%20these%20remain%20in%20legal%20limbo.%20If%20the%20family%20were%20to%20pursue%20legal%20action%2C%20the%20declaration%20would%20determine%20the%20type%20of%20lawsuit%20and%20poten