al%20probe%20and%20prepared%20a%20list%20of%20those%20linked%20to%20multiple%20IP%20addresses%20and%20are%20suspected%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20visa%20consultants%2C%20document%20vendors%2C%20passport%20delivery%20addresses%2C%20and%20education%20consultants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20named%20over%2030%20suspects%20-%20agents%20and%20applicants%20who%20allegedly%20tried%20to%20obtain%20a%20visa%20using%20fake%20documents.%20It%20shared%20several%20instances%20of%20applicants%20submitting%20forged%20documents%2C%20in%20which%20the%20applicants%20claimed%20not%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20documents%20submitted%20in%20their%20application%20and%20those%20were%20created%20by%20their%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20is%20being%20investigated%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20from%20the%20US%20embassy%20follows%20a%20crackdown%20by%20the%20Trump%20administration%20on%20immigrants%20entering%20the%20country%20by%20illegal%20means.%20Thousands%20have%20been%20deported%20since%20Donald%20Trump%20came%20to%20power%20two%20months%20ago%2C%20riding%20on%20his%20promises%20to%20secure%20American%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crackdown%20has%20also%20brought%20to%20focus%20the%20desperate%20means%20by%20which%20hundreds%20of%20men%20and%20women%20in%20third-world%20countries%20try%20to%20reach%20the%20US.%20Many%20have%20undertaken%20the%20long%20'donkey'%20route%20passing%20through%20multiple%20countries%20and%20treacherous%20forests%2C%20and%20many%20have%20perished%20in%20their%20quest%20for%20the%20American%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742532480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fjjnqk3vo_us-embassy_625x300_21_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpolice-case-against-passport-agents-after-us-embassy-flags-visa-fraud-7972963%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Police%20have%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20several%20visa%20and%20passport%