22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esent%20quantum%20stocks%20tumbling%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239329433-af17-40a4-81e5-abe6858bac4b%5C%22%3EQuantum%20blockchain%20architecture%20from%20D-Wave%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPalo%20Alto-based%20D-Wave%20announced%20the%20publication%20of%20its%20latest%20paper%2C%20which%20introduced%20a%20new%20quantum%20blockchain%20architecture.%20The%20paper%20outlines%20how%20the%20company%20built%20and%20tested%20a%20%26quot%3Bproof%20of%20quantum%26quot%3B%20algorithm%20that%20uses%20quantum%20computation%20to%20generate%20and%20validate%20blockchain%20hashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20in%20the%20field%20agree%20quantum%20computing%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-cybersecurity-threat-break-encryption-cryptocurrency-bitcoin-blockchain-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eend%20encryption%20as%20we%20know%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20resulting%20in%20massive%20security%20risks%20for%20any%20private%20data%20stored%20on%20the%20internet.%C2%A0D-Wave's%20research%2C%20the%20company%20says%2C%20could%20help%20power%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20blockchain%20for%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20supply%20chain%20management%2C%20healthcare%2C%20identity%20verification%2C%20and%20decentralized%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20performed%20connotations%20that%20your%20GPUs%20can't%20perform%2C%20and%20now%20we're%20able%20to%20build%20a%20blockchain%20that's%20more%20energy%20efficient%20than%20what's%20running%20on%20GPUs%2C%26quot%3B%20Alan%20Baratz%2C%20CEO%20of%20D-Wave%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227c5fe69e-48e8-40a1-b3d9-0174e62287e6%5C%22%3EContextual%20Machine%20Learning%20from%20Infleqtion%20and%20Nvidia%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInfleqtion%2C%20a%20quantum%20information%20technology%20company%2C%20unveiled%20its%20new%20machine%20learning%20approach%2C%20called%20Contextual%20Machine%20Learning%2C%20during%20Quantum%20Day.%20The%20CML%20approach%20was%20developed%20in%20partnership%20with%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CML%20approach%20leverages%20quantum%20computing%20to%20enhance%20artificial%20intelligence.%20It%20allows%20machine%20learning%20models%20to%20process%20more%20information%20over%20longer%20time%20periods%20and%20from%20multiple%20sources%20simultaneously%2C%20enhancing%20AI's%20ability%20to%20recognize%20patterns%20in%20sensor%20data%2C%20predict%20trends%2C%20and%20make%20real-time%20decisions%20with%20greater%20accuracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b49d0118-0c8b-4dda-a4c6-ffa608108f38%5C%22%3EClassical-Quantum%20interface%20from%20SEEQC%20and%20Nvidia%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20quantum%20hardware%20manufacturer%20SEEQC%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20Nvidia%2C%20announced%20the%20world's%20first%20fully%20digital%20quantum-classical%20interface%20demo%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0a%20milestone%20toward%20delivering%20the%20first%20chip-to-chip%20interface%20that%20will%20connect%20quantum%20processors%20with%20classical%20GPUs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we've%20done%20is%20we've%20taken%20the%20core%20functionality%20of%20a%20quantum%20computer%2C%20put%20it%20on%20a%20chip%2C%20and%20then%20made%20that%20chip%20operate%20at%20the%20same%20temperature%20of%20qubits%20so%20that%20we%20can%20actually%20put%20them%20together%20and%20create%20the%20connectivity%20that%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20SEEQC%20CEO%20John%20Levy%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prototype%20chip%20relies%20on%20the%20strengths%20of%20classical%20computing%20to%20handle%20error%20correction%20in%20real%20time%20while%20leveraging%20the%20strengths%20of%20quantum%20computing%20to%20process%20more%20data%20more%20quickly%20than%20classical%20computers%20alone%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20insight%20is%20that%20we're%20doing%20it%20in%20a%20very%20power-efficient%20way%20because%20if%20you%20use%20regular%20chips%2C%20the%20heat%20of%20those%20chips%20w