0wildlife%2C%20it%20changed%20these%20children%E2%80%99s%20lives.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20showed%20them%20a%20new%20way%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20natural%20world%20around%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamreen%20shares%20that%20Roundglass%20Sustain%20is%20also%20working%20with%20the%20youth%20in%20these%20communities%20and%20through%20their%20workshops%2C%20encouraging%20them%20to%20stand%20in%20solidarity%20with%20their%20native%20wildlife.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Wings%20of%20Hope%3A%20A%20Bustling%20Village%20and%20Their%20Bird%20Friends%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMenar%20is%20proof%20that%20conservation%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20always%20have%20to%20come%20from%20big%20organisations%20or%20governments.%20Real%20change%20can%20start%20with%20a%20community%20that%20decides%20to%20take%20care%20of%20its%20backyard%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gunjan%20Menon%20about%20the%20Rajasthan%20village%20that%20she%20featured%20in%20her%20documentary%20%3Cem%3EWings%20of%20Hope%3A%20A%20Bustling%20Village%20and%20Their%20Bird%20Friends%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20films%20have%20won%20over%2032%20International%20awards%20and%20nominations%20across%2013%20countries%20for%20their%20powerful%20narratives%20which%20touch%20upon%20conservation%20and%20human-wildlife%20coexistence.%20A%20believer%20that%20impact%20following%20a%20film%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20didactic%2C%20but%20spark%20real%20change%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20Gunjan%20says%20Menar%20is%20a%20perfect%20example.%20The%20village%20has%20become%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F3735%2Fmangalajodi-village-of-bird-protectors